Dialogs.Dialog: Ah, right. What type of girl do you like？
The type of girl that I like？ Hmm, if I have to say...
I think I like an intellectual and strong girl.
Like a smart girl who likes to say what she wants？
Yeah, yeah. That kind of girl.
Who sometimes likes to tease you？
Hmm？ I see. So some teasing would be fine, huh？
The kind and positive type, I think.
The type that usually does whatever you ask？
Then would an upperclassman be okay？
For that... I guess it's okay.
I see. So I shouldn't have been worried then...
I mean the calm and mature type.
Ah... Um, I see. I got it. Thanks.
...Sorry, I feel a little embarrassed to say that.
Hehe... Me, too. I think I feel a little embarrassed, too.
By the way, can you tell me honestly what type of girl you like？
Honestly...？ Hmm, the type that I like is...
The kind and obedient type, I think. I don't like a boisterous girl.
So, you like a calm and mature girl？
Hmm, then will it be fine like this...？
You usually express your feelings clearly.
You don't mind that I tease you sometimes？
Hmm, I see... Okay, thanks for your answer.
By the way, what type of girl do you like？
My type？ Well, let me think...
The kind and obedient type, I think.
The type that usually does whatever you ask？
No, I've just never imagined you as the type that likes to take the lead.
Hehe, kind and obedient, huh？ So, you like a girl who always follows your lead, right？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. You're my ideal woman, I think.
Geez... Don't flatter me like that...
I didn't flatter you. You are kind and broad-minded. I really like this kind of girl.
It's kind of embarrassing to say this though.
Hehe. Are you embarrassed？ You're so cute.
What's the matter？ Did something happen？
No, it's not like that. The movie...
I was so impressed with the movie I just saw... When I thought about it, I started crying.
I see. So ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, do you feel sympathy for the characters in that movie？
Usually, I'm not like this. But this time, it's different.
A movie that can make you cry just by thinking about it... It must be a good movie.
What kind of movie is it？
It's about pure love. A female teacher has fallen in love with her student.
I see. So you feel sympathy with that teacher？
Ah, I have to go. My face is a mess now. Bye.
(...Okay, not many customers now. I'll take a break.)
Okay, Nene-chan. You're so cute！ He'll surely fall madly in love with you！
Um, somehow... What were you doing？
Well, um... Right！ It was an appearance check！ Like checking the uniform, and hair, and stuff.
Ah, that's important for a restaurant, right？
But, then... What about falling madly in love...？
That's... a reminder that we can't fall madly in love with the customers！
Ah, I have to go！ See you！
Okay, I'll keep working hard again today！
Well, I have a favor to ask of you.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ is asking for my help？ This is rare. What is it？
The manager asked me to do this, but...
Fine. I know ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ already has plenty of things to take care of.
Ah, really？ Now, I've become such an able man.
Hey, don't get ahead of yourself.
But, maybe I shall ask you to help with something else, too.
There's this... And that... If you can do them all, that will be helpful.
Hehe, I'm kidding. But, you've been working hard lately. Maybe I should give you a reward.
...Are you imagining something perverted？ A kid like this doesn't deserve a reward then.
No, it's nothing. This coffee is just too hot.
Is that so？ I was startled.
I can't handle hot food. Sorry if I scared you.
Hmm？ That's unexpected from a perfect woman like ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲.
Just because I can't handle hot food...？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ has weak points, too！ I've found one！
Saying it like that, you aren't cute at all.
Occasionally, it's my turn to retaliate.
Earlier, there was a wrong order for a pizza, and you secretly ate it.
And you haven't washed your uniform since last week, right？ The manager will be very angry if he knows this.
There are more. Do you want to hear？
Hmm... I'm going back to work！
▲主人公＊▲. Are you about to leave？
Me, too. Ah... You button is falling off, see？
You're right. It's okay, though. Just leave it like that.
(▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ really is such a beautiful girl.)
For something like this, you could've asked for my help.
(Also, she's very good at taking care of things...)
Thanks. ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, you're good at sewing, too.
No, I'm a woman, so this is just natural.
But, you got it done in no time.
What？ You wanted me to stay like that longer then？
Now, this big sister has to get going. Be careful on your way home, okay？
Raise you head. I'll hold your nose for you.
I'm fine. Just put some tissue on it and I'll be fine...
No, you'll bleed again when you take the tissue off.
It's fine. Just be a little obedient, okay？
(Did I fall asleep on her lap...？)
(It hurts, but somehow I feel so lucky.)
Urgh, out. Sorry. I'll get the ball.
You're welcome. So guys and girls are practicing together in this club.
I think it's good like this for our club.
Hmm... And, that girl is very pretty, huh？
No, never mind. See you later. Do your best.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, you're also here. I didn't see you.
Look, that girl right there is my teammate in the tennis club. I was about to call out to her.
When ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ called me, I was really surprised.
I see. So, I interrupted you, huh？
No, you didn't. I didn't really have any business with her.
Never mind. I'm leaving. You'd better go talk with that girl.
(She's gone... There's nothing she should get upset about.)
(Once I'm done with this, I'll have to sweep the other side then...)
Not at all. This is just a piece of cake.
I see. I shouldn't bother you while you're working. I'll get going now.
All right. I think I'm done with this.
This area is not clean yet. You have to redo it.
Isn't it okay？ This is just a piece of cake, isn't it？
I'll get some disinfectant and bandages for you.
Did you get injured？ Shall I take care of your wounds for you？
It's okay. My teammate is getting a first aid kit for me. But, I...
It wouldn't be good to bother someone outside the tennis club to do this.
Geez. Just let that girl take care of you then！
(Did I say something to make her angry？)
▲主人公＊▲, When you finish sorting this shelf, can you help me over there？
I'll leave it to you then.
All right, I'd better hurry and get this done.
No, I came to return a book. ...That girl is cute, huh？
You think so？ She's a first year student, but as a library committee, she's my senior.
So she's like your supervisor then？
Ah, geez. I can never finish these lending records！
Because you've left them undone for a long time.
Shut up already. Just help me do it.
She should learn from her mistakes. I can't spoil her. This is for her sake.
Well, we have to work together as library committee members.
▲小早川＊▲. What are you doing here？
None of your business. Are you my dad or what？
Again, are you my dad or what！？
Oh my, if I don't scold her a little bit, she won't like it, huh？
Who do you want to scold？
No one likes to be scolded by older people, you know？
Yeah. Have you ever thought that I caused troubles for you？
(What is it that ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ is worried about...？)
Could it be that you come here to see me？
How could that be？ Are you an idiot？
For me, you are the reason I continue working here.
Geez, of course it was a joke.
Not that the whole thing is a joke though.
Today will be your last day to work at Dixie's, right？
Yeah, thanks for your help up until now.
Ever since you've started working there, you've helped me a lot.
Of course. And since then, I've enjoyed my job even more.
Really？ I also enjoyed working there.
Hehe, next time, visit us as a customer, okay？
See you later. I'm really happy to have a little brother like you.
(Right, she's like an older sister to me...)
Yeah, it's one year after ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲'s.
Um, right. I should have gathered up my courage before I graduated.
But, it's time for us to part.
I can't continue acting like your older sister...
I am now graduated from being your sister...
